Create timestamps and save important moments from a video.Play any youtube video click on the add icon present in the  youtube player left control to add any timestamp.To play the time stamp again just click on the extension and select your timestamp.

Timestamp icon is  created by Freepik - Flaticon .Check out more such icons here:- https://www.flaticon.com/free-icons/timestamp
